# Title: Active Directory Structure Export Via Ldifde.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-03-14
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the execution of "ldifde.exe" in order to export organizational Active Directory structure.
# MITRE Tactic: Exfiltration
# Tags: attack.exfiltration
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_ldifde_export.yml

CommandLine="*-f*" Image="*\\ldifde.exe" OR OriginalFileName="ldifde.exe" NOT CommandLine="* -i*"